	<str name="Title">
		Gas Sparging
	</str>
	<str name="Abstract">
		The invention relates to a method for operating interacting different units, particularly of an installation, with different controllers that control these advanced control sequences, particularly with different control pulses. The inventive method is characterized in that the clock pulses (IPO.sub.i) of the different controllers (3.1, 3.2, 3.3) are interpolated to a common system clock pulse (t.sub.Tiex), and that the control sequences are synchronized. A device suited for carrying out the inventive method correspondingly comprises at least one common interpolation device (5.3) for the controllers (3.1, 3.2., 3.3) for interpolating the clock pulses (IPO.sub.i) of the different controllers (3.1, 3.2, 3.3) to a common system clock pulse (t.sub.Tiex) and at least one synchronization device (5) for synchronizing the control sequences.
	</str>
